The Potshots application is written in Python, it requires python 3 to run.
The site is hosted at potshots.pshome.me it may be easier to just visit it there.

If you want to run potshots locally here are the instructions:
1. install python 3 for mac os: https://www.python.org/downloads/macos/
2. run: pip install -r requirements.txt
3. in terminal: python3 desktop_app.py

